{"tid":1152867,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"（林欣彤）許廷鏗拉攏簽華納，林欣彤「復出」有望","createTime":"2019-05-13T09:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T01:33:24.000Z","uid":133304,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0af56abfce055a80a76f1983706828fef606465","tid":1152867,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"歌手林欣彤（Mag）去年因為聲帶問題，取消原定12月舉行的處女個唱，更全面停工養聲，到3月下旬以表演嘉賓身份亮相好友許廷鏗（Alfred）演唱會，才正式同歌迷見面。當大家以為Mag「小巨肺」實力恢復後復出有期，她上月初卻在網上宣布與王祖藍旗下公司3年合約已滿，令人擔心她「復出」無期。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，Mag今日正式公布已和華納唱片簽訂合約，成為「華納一哥」Alfred的師妹，有傳Alfred積極拉攏才撮成今次合作。其實她再戰樂壇早有迹可尋，日前她在IG上載整頭髮的相片，留言：「新人事、新作風、新髮型」據知她已進行新歌錄音，且飛抵日本拍MV。"},{"pid":"767923caa8f4c3695a870a222972b8ea0a8474ff","tid":1152867,"uid":29938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c636c04754a0291d2789daf2e47a242dafa7272","tid":1152867,"uid":240599,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"Mag is worth to be famous. She sings well."},{"pid":"b1675024ddd51e22269929ef0526568edcedcde3","tid":1152867,"uid":37358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"佢唱多啲本身的用處嗰啲style 啦"},{"pid":"94b76c761f880263ce13be7c9bb5d7caadcb5750","tid":1152867,"uid":186189,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T19:01:16.000Z","msg":"仲有公司敢簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d660654c6fd39e78d8b0db67aace678c27fad2","tid":1152867,"uid":68641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T19:44:55.000Z","msg":"一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7b84b23bc27b27d3f8934c5be9e0df23e64dd2","tid":1152867,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"出咗新歌"},{"pid":"209926be548423d4fff06cfbcc83016c34e444e8","tid":1152